   - Gender: {!rec_LabOrder.Patient__r.Gender__c}
   - Date of Birth: {!rec_LabOrder.Patient__r.DateOfBirth__c}

🔹 Lab Order Information
   - Name: {!rec_LabOrder.First_Name__c} {!rec_LabOrder.Last_Name__c}
   - Gender: {!rec_LabOrder.Gender__c}
   - Date of Birth: {!rec_LabOrder.Date_of_Birth__c}

Please reach out to the patient if you need to confirm their demographic information.
To make corrections and re-submit the order, click &quot;Update Order&quot; at the top of the Lab Order page to enter the updated details.</text>
